/>\n實可商業區(Sedco Complex)的Sri Selera Kampung Air廣場，必有稱心如意的發現，這是一處由數家海鮮餐廳共同營運的美食天堂。<br />\n<br />\n對蟹、蝦情有獨鍾的老饕，座落在林達斯廣場(Lintas Square)的香江餐廳（電話+60 88-254927）<br />\n<br />\n丹容亞路第一海濱(Tanjung Aru First Beach)的丹容亞路海鮮餐廳（Tanjung Aru Seafood Restaurant, 電話+60 88-246911）<br />\n<br />\n海邊燒烤（Beach BBQ, 電話+60 88－246911 ）<br />\n<br />\n丹容亞路末沙烈路(Mat Salleh Road, Tanjung Aru)的海龍城餐廳（電話+60 88-215555）"},{"pid":"3bafa72df997cee7f06fe8f9d424a50a2c6e2839","tid":714524,"uid":23560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T03:14:47.000Z","msg":"肉骨茶同喇沙要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇戲好平可以試吓玩d-box<br />\n香港貴幾倍<br />\n<br />\n文化村幾搞笑可以玩吓<br />\n<br />\n外島我無去<br />\n但聽同事講好多烏蠅<br />\n自己衡量<br />\n<br />\n我嗰時懶無係local旅行社報tour<br />\n直接用沙巴遊搵agent<br />\n嗰次個領隊識廣東話純利溝通<br />\n價錢有可能會貴啲啩<br />\n<br />\n出入交通用grab就得"},{"pid":"1fc307d500eeff23fd5c67f9558de9575908f48f","tid":714524,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b6a6bda35c2ed0378e5178b9830d4b415482a67","tid":714524,"uid":25486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"丹絨亞路海灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"D大媽多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551ac6e313038e8f5d18446455683ee68bbde6b9","tid":714524,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"Imago入面有間機鋪好撚平"},{"pid":"5c42efe472c9473cadd31cf4005081e4a7c12f81","tid":714524,"uid":166986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"即係去個到報啲tour會平啲？"},{"pid":"9092967a48dc1687543b2b2a6ddb6fea37d8b022","tid":714524,"uid":72177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"去香格里拉個sunset bar"},{"pid":"348f0d01e6b201fe96d1fab709430be90b38ac48","tid":714524,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"